title: ARY News Headlines | PM Imran Khan forms committee to reach out JUI-F | 11 AM | 17 October 2019
text:
ARY News Headlines | PM Imran Khan forms committee to reach out JUI-F | 11 AM | 17 October 2019

#PMImranKhan #KamyabJawan #PTI

– PM Imran Khan to launch the ‘Kamyab Jawan Programme’ for youth welfare today.

– JUI-F Azadi March: Pervez Khattak to lead PTI committee for talks with Maulana Fazlur Rehman.

– Royal couple Prince William, Princess Kate Middleton to visit Lahore Today, Badshahi mosque decorated for a warm welcome.

– US President Donald Trump’s letter to President of Turkey Recep Tayyip Erdogan breaks political norms.

– Polling for PS-11-Larkana-II by-election underway, a strong contest between Moazim Ali Abbasi and Jamil Somroo.

– T10 Cricket league: UAE’s Mohammad Naveed, Shaiman Anwar, Qadeer Ahmed removed from the final qualifying round for corruption charges.
